<Base
  title="About Classroom Stack"
  description="Who is behind Classroom Stack and how we test AI teaching and study tools."
>
  <h1>About Classroom Stack</h1>
  <p>
    Classroom Stack reviews AI tools for teachers, tutors, and students. Our
    method is simple: we sign up, run each tool through real teaching and study
    tasks — an actual lesson plan, a real quiz on a real syllabus, genuine essay
    feedback — and report what happened, including the failures.
  </p>
  <p>
    We publish what we would tell a colleague: which tool to pick for your
    situation, what it costs, and what the marketing page doesn't mention.
  </p>
  <p>See how we make money on the <a href="/disclosure">disclosure page</a>.</p>
</Base>
